00:59:15,666 --> 00:59:16,959
We'll have a talk tomorrow.

780
00:59:17,585 --> 00:59:19,920
I will use all of my status
and authority

781
00:59:21,213 --> 00:59:23,966
and make you pay for this.

782
00:59:29,555 --> 00:59:30,681
You're so heavy.

783
00:59:41,817 --> 00:59:45,529
Mr. Noh, will you wake up? Please!

784
00:59:48,866 --> 00:59:51,327
I'm sure
your unconscious mind remembers.

785
00:59:51,410 --> 00:59:54,747
Press the code. Here. Do it.

786
01:00:14,517 --> 01:00:17,436
FILING FOR LOVE

787
01:00:18,020 --> 01:00:20,815
GUEST APPEARANCE
BY HWANG HEE AND KIM YE-WON

788
01:00:45,548 --> 01:00:46,715
How are you feeling, Ms. Joo?

789
01:00:46,799 --> 01:00:48,717
What is this, Ki-jun?

790
01:00:48,801 --> 01:00:51,053
Is there a reason
why Joo In-a can't find out

791
01:00:51,136 --> 01:00:52,137
about our relationship?

792
01:00:52,805 --> 01:00:54,014
It's your personal life.

793
01:00:54,098 --> 01:00:55,891
Something like this cannot...

794
01:00:55,975 --> 01:00:57,101
I said, cannot distract me.

795
01:00:57,184 --> 01:00:58,811
Do you not care
about my personal life?

796
01:00:59,854 --> 01:01:01,105
You even kissed me.

797
01:01:01,772 --> 01:01:04,400
Stop feigning ignorance.
You already know.

798
01:01:04,817 --> 01:01:06,861
About your question, Mr. Noh...

799
01:01:06,944 --> 01:01:09,113
The real reason
why I keep pushing you away...

800
01:01:09,738 --> 01:01:10,990
I...

801
01:01:11,073 --> 01:01:12,116
Ms. Joo!

802
01:01:13,742 --> 01:01:15,369
I've lost a bit of my mind

803
01:01:15,828 --> 01:01:17,037
because of you.

804
01:01:30,050 --> 01:01:32,052
Subtitles by Eunsook Youn
and Jennifer Lim
